NO HOA!! 
Newer roof, windows. Newer appliances. Plantation shutters in living areas. Brand new carpet in bedrooms. Whole interior freshly painted.  Pergola and patio pavers off the Arizona room. Oversized 2 car garage with AC. 
Leased solar. This home is perfect for the retirement lifestyle you want to live. Sun City West offers lots of amenities heated swimming pools, pickleball courts, tennis, fitness centers. Golf courses and much more!!  Highly motivated seller!!!!!
BRING YOUR OFFERS!!!!
